Containing: Anti-human immunoglobulins conjugated to horseradish peroxidase

Stop Solution 1 vial, 15ml (capped white: colorless solution)
Containing: 1M Hydrochloric Acid
Microtiterplate 12x8 well strips with breakaway microwells
